version_description: We’ve moved our profile section to the main navigation to give you more convenient access to your settings and order details. We’ve also brought in autoplay so you can preview videos sooner.
We’ve upped our game. Keep an eye out for some exciting things coming up soon.
Bug fixes.
We've improved the way you navigate Shop and quashed some bugs.
We've introduced a new way to navigate our most immersive stories, and evolved the sharing experience among other improvements.
General enhancements and bug fixes
We've introduced performance improvements for an even better experience in our CONFIRMED app. This includes finding and navigating stories.
For this release we've brought in new ways to shop along with bug fixes. Happy New Year from the CONFIRMED team!
